## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on citizen journalism. The perspectives gathered are primarily from online articles and opinion pieces, which may not fully capture the academic discourse on the subject. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of digital media means that the landscape of citizen journalism is continually changing, potentially affecting the relevance of the findings over time.